    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>A material of white to light gray or light yellow color, extremely lightweight, absorbent, and compact, that is found in Asia Minor and is used for making tobacco pipes and ornamental carvings.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
